step 1  : project structure 
-> npm init
-> create index.js
-> npm express morgan nodemomn ejs body-parser dotenv mongoose axios
-> change node -> nodemoon in package.json
-> create project structure :
    -> create assets inside assets folder create (css , js , img)
    -> create views inside this all html file using ejs to create dynamic html
    -> create server folder for model,  mongodb connection 
        -- in this project we are using mvc(model , view and controller) pattern : application desgin pattern that seprate        application data and bussniess logic
    -> create model  controller , routes , services , database folder inside server folder 
        -- model : we can perform data validation , processing data ,creating mongoschema
        -- controller : user request for resources from the server
